org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode

Class INode.QuotaDelta

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.INode.QuotaDelta
  • Enclosing class:
    org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.INode

    public static class INode.QuotaDelta
extends Object
    Information used to record quota usage delta. This data structure is usually passed along with an operation like INode.cleanSubtree(org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.INode.ReclaimContext, int, int). Note that after the operation the delta counts should be decremented from the ancestral directories' quota usage.
